OL,4,CBrewdog reveals plans for beer-themed
OL,5,Chotel in Edinburgh
OL,6, Brewdog, the Scottish brewer and pub
OL,7, chain, has announced plans for a
OL,8, beer-themed hotel in Edinburgh's Old
OL,9, Town.
OL,11,FThe Doghouse-branded boutique hotel
OL,12,Fwill be in a former school opposite the
OL,13,Fcity council headquarters on Market
OL,14,FStreet.
OL,16,F"Expect beer on tap in all the rooms,
OL,17,Fmini-bars filled with the best beers in
OL,18,Fthe planet and fridges in the shower
OL,19,Ffor shower beers," co-founder James
OL,20,FWatt said.
